issue.title: Add html + basic ws implementation
issue.body:
The ws is responsible for automating the authentication process in order
to retrieve the token. It is required to request TransferWise team to
enable redirect to our localhost.

Currently the request for the token returns a 400 response:
{"error":"invalid_grant","error_description":"Redirect URI mismatch."}
because the url we are redirecting is not accepted by their system
